org.opends.server.admin.std.client

Interface EntryUUIDPluginCfgClient

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ConfigurationClient, PluginCfgClient

    public interface EntryUUIDPluginCfgClient
extends PluginCfgClient
    A client-side interface for reading and modifying Entry UUID Plugin settings.

    The Entry UUID Plugin generates values for the entryUUID operational attribute whenever an entry is added via protocol or imported from LDIF.
